Larroud=C3=A9=E2=80=99s accordioned supply chain dramatically reduced the r=
isk of a wholesale partner
ending up with shoes nobody wants. =E2=80=9CWe are able to produce in betwe=
en two and three weeks=E2=80=99 time,=E2=80=9D Marina told me. =E2=80=9CWhi=
ch is insane if you compare it to the major footwear brands. They take at l=
east six months, sometimes a year, to get a reorder in, right? So we really=
 changed the game in that sense.=E2=80=9D The strategy had other perks, too=
=2E =E2=80=9CIf they have a shoe that is n=
ot selling, and they decide to put=20=
that on a markdown, at the end of the day it=E2=80=99s jeopardizing our bra=
nd,=E2=80=9D Marina said. =E2=80=9CSo for us,
