 everything is going to be okay, noting that the company still has =E2=80=
=9Cwork to do=E2=80=9D on Dior,
and that Richemont=E2=80=99s numbers were <em>so</em> good that it made LVM=
H=E2=80=99s output look less impressive by comparison. From my view, it=E2=
=80=99s important to remember that the only apples-to-apples comparison her=
