s a seemingly small pivot, but also a big one in a hidebound industry. =E2=
=80=9CI do think it takes someone who is an outsider,=E2=80=9D Marina told =
me recently, regarding the couple=E2=80=99s decision to drop-ship-ify their=
 wholesale
